msgid "**Filtered**"
msgstr "**Filtruotas**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudextraction.rst:302
msgid ""
"Specify the point cloud file to export the data to. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Nurodykite taškų masyvo failą, į kurį reikia eksportuoti duomenis. "
":ref:`Vienas iš <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudextraction.rst:323
msgid ""
"Output point cloud layer with the filtered features of the input point cloud"
" layer. Currently supported formats are :file:`.LAS`, :file:`.LAZ`, "
":file:`.COPC.LAZ` and :file:`.VPC`."
msgstr ""
"Išvesties taškų masyvo sluoksnis su filtruotais įvesties taškų masyvo "
"sluoksnio geoobjektais. Šiuo metu palaikomi formatai yra :file:`.LAS`, "
":file:`.LAZ`, :file:`.COPC.LAZ` ir :file:`.VPC`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointcloudextraction.rst:329
